Sprawling lawns and trees, with a Central Rose Garden, Public Children's Park & Swimming Pool, this place has something on offer for almost everyone.

The hundreds of varieties of flora and a walking track outlined by a canal with ducks and occasional boats, make this picturesque garden ideal to spend the evening.</blockquote>
